          "_name": "features13",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"features13\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitles\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <select title=\"Cards\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>3</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"../_images/img/06.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#f9f9f9\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">Algunos de nuetros clientes</h2>\n\n        <div class=\"media-container-row container\" mbr-cards=\"bootstrap\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-md-6 p-5 m-3 align-center\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"card-img\">\n                    <a href=\"https://www.formavital.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/forma-vital-300x200.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title></a>\n                </div>\n                <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\">\n                    Forma Vital</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">\n                    Sitio dedicado a la Auriculoterapia</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-md-6 p-5 m-3 align-center\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 1\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"card-img\">\n                    <a href=\"http://oftalmologoretina.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/oftalmologo-retina-300x200.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title></a>\n                </div>\n                <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\">\n                    Oftalmólogo retina</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">\n                    Sitio dedicado al cuidado de los ojos</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-md-6 p-5 m-3 align-center\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"card-img\">\n                    <a href=\"https://energy-dance-studio.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/energy-dance-studio-300x200.png\" alt=\"Mobirise\" title></a>\n                </div>\n                <h4 class=\"card-title py-2 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\">\n                    Energi Dance Studio</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">\n                    Sitio dedicado al entrenamiento personal</p>\n            </div>    \n        </div>\n</div></section>",
